- **Leverage reproducible builds** to detect a compromise in our infrastructure ([[!tails_ticket 14455]])
- **Switch to Wayland** ([[!tails_ticket 12213]])
- **Research Flatpak (or similar) for sandboxing** ([[!tails_ticket 15874]])

